## API Components

### ApiEndpoint
```mdx
<ApiEndpoint method="GET" path="/api/endpoint" description="Description">
  <ApiParams>
    <ApiParam name="param" type="string" required description="Param desc" />
  </ApiParams>
  <ApiResponse status={200} description="Success">
    ```json
    { "result": "value" }
    ```
  </ApiResponse>
</ApiEndpoint>
```

